author: Lane Florsheim
title: Shanelle Nyasiase is a Model to Watch
text:
GROWING UP, Shanelle Nyasiase wanted to be a flight attendant so that she could travel the world. Now, the 21-year-old South Sudanese model finds herself on planes more often than she would like. “It’s great to see places I could only have dreamt of,” she wrote by email, “but being away from friends and family can be tough, as well as jet lag.”
Nyasiase lives in Nairobi, Kenya, but finds herself at home less and less after her breakout success walking the Miu Miu runway in fall 2017. During the most recent season, in February...
